You see a yellow notice of construction:

                  NOTICE OF CONSTRUCTION

Due to poor quality and safety tests, the elven quick car terminals
have been permanently closed for the safety of all people.  Please
use overland routes to get to your destination.  The dwarves are 
busy building new scenario for your enjoyment.  My apologies for
this inconvenience.

                                     Caledon

Another sign below the notice reads:

Dwarves needed for excavation of mountainous terrain.  Please inquire.

